Package jakarta.validation.constraints

Annotation Interface NotBlank

@Documented @Constraint(validatedBy={}) @Target({METHOD,FIELD,ANNOTATION_TYPE,CONSTRUCTOR,PARAMETER,TYPE_USE}) @Retention(RUNTIME) @Repeatable(List.class) public @interface NotBlank
The annotated element must not be null and must contain at least one non-whitespace character. Accepts CharSequence.
Since:
2.0
Author:
Hardy Ferentschik
